                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                />
              </svg>
              Platform acara dan webinar profesional
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              <svg
                class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                />
              </svg>
              Papan lowongan kerja sektor GLAM
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              <svg
                class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                />
              </svg>
              Bursa Koleksi. Donasikan yang tidak terpakai, cari yang dibutuhkan.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20 border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-700 rounded-xl p-4">
            <h5 class="text-sm font-semibold text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-300 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">
              Curatorian, <span class="italic">where the curatorians meet.</span>
            </h5>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              merupakan sistem jejaring sosial profesional untuk praktisi GLAM Indonesia, dibangun
              menggunakan Elixir dan Phoenix Framework. Lisensi Apache 2.0, kode sumber tersedia di
              GitHub, dan kami menyambut kontribusi dari pengembang mana pun.
            </p>
            <div class="flex w-full text-center">
              <.link
                href="https://github.com/curatorian/curatorian"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
                class="btn-primary w-full"
              >
                Lihat <span class="italic">Source Code </span> di GitHub
              </.link>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%!-- Janji gratis --%>
      <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 border border-green-200 dark:border-green-800 rounded-xl p-6 flex items-center gap-5">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/50 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
