        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Curatorian mendukung berbagai vocabulary metadata untuk Gallery, Library, Archive, dan Museum. Berikut prefix (namespace) dan nama standarnya.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        <div class="border rounded-lg p-3">
          <code class="font-mono text-violet-600">dcterms</code> Dublin Core Terms
        </div>
